Package: rszvec
Title: Simple R Interface to the zvec Vector Database
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Bartek", "Szabat", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "keneo@szabat.com")
Description: A minimal, R-native interface to the zvec vector database.
    Wraps 'rzvec' with five functions covering the core workflow: open a
    collection, add vectors (one at a time or in bulk from a matrix), search
    for nearest neighbours, and delete documents. Results are returned as
    plain R data frames.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
SystemRequirements: Python (>= 3.10), zvec Python package
Imports:
    rzvec
Remotes:
    keneo/play-zvec/rzvec
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    withr
Config/testthat/edition: 3
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
